# Phase 13: Feature Completion - Settings & Library

## Goal Description
Connect the Settings page to real user data to allow profile customization. Fix broken sidebar navigation links and implement the "Liked Videos" library page.

## Proposed Changes

### Settings Page
#### [MODIFY] [app/settings/page.tsx](file:///C:/GoLive/app/settings/page.tsx)
- Fetch current user profile from `profiles` table.
- Populate inputs with real data.
- Implement `updateProfile` function to save changes to Supabase.
- Add Avatar upload (or robust URL input for now).

### Navigation
#### [MODIFY] [components/Sidebar.tsx](file:///C:/GoLive/components/Sidebar.tsx)
